mil.nga.geopackage.io

Class FeatureTileGen

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.geopackage.io.FeatureTileGen

  • public class FeatureTileGen
extends Object
    Feature Tile Generator main method for command line feature to tile generation. Generate tiles from a feature table. To run from command line, build with the standalone profile: mvn clean install -Pstandalone java -classpath geopackage-*-standalone.jar mil.nga.geopackage.io.FeatureTileGen +usage_arguments
    Since:
    1.1.2
    Author:
    osbornb
